    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828740/extras/03306a6975c35e52e63b152c1e996578.avif?t=1754148860\" width=571 height=157 /></span><br>Join Kai, the super dense MC, in his daily life as he slowly figures out that his childhood friends might have crushes on him...?<br><br><strong>NEMESIS GAVIN</strong><br>Kai has been picked on by Gavin ever since they were kids.<br>Due to being constantly mocked by his nemesis, he's tried his best to change his appearance to be more intimidating.<br>Gavin's only motive is to get Kai's attention, but instead, he's now hated by his crush.<br><br><strong>HERO PERCY</strong><br>Percy, on the other hand, is always there at the right time to defend Kai.<br>His kind, yet over-protective title led him to become Kai's best friend.<br>For all these years, Percy has yearned to be something more than friends, but his attempts so far have been futile.<br><br>Both Gavin and Percy act the way they do because they're absolutely smitten with Kai. Unfortunately, Kai is too dense to notice their affection!<br>He just wants to fall in love with someone... But will he ever consider dating his best friend or rival?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828740/extras/743c97e8369fb15983aa64be3c76df30.avif?t=1754148860\" width=571 height=157 /></span><br>- SFW. Pure Fluff and Comedy to make you smile!<br>- Your choices decide which Love Interest you interact with!<br>- 30K words<br>- 3 routes/endings and 18 CGs to unlock!<br>- Go on dates<br>- Send text messages<br>- Partake in silly banter<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828740/extras/ff6dd92ef842dc0995ee5a6f1c984e26.avif?t=1754148860\" width=571 height=157 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_